net.sf.mpxj.phoenix

Class DatatypeConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.mpxj.phoenix.DatatypeConverter

  • public final class DatatypeConverter
extends Object
    This class contains methods used to perform the datatype conversions required to read and write Phoenix files.
